                  Test Firestore
                </button>
                <button
                  type="button"
                  id="cleanup-drafts-btn"
                  class="px-4 py-2 bg-red-600 hover:bg-red-500 text-white text-sm font-medium rounded-md shadow-md transition-colors duration-300"
                >
                  Limpiar Borradores
